DELIMITER $$
CREATE TRIGGER `validate_order_status` BEFORE UPDATE ON `orders` FOR EACH ROW BEGIN
    -- Only allow valid status transitions
    IF OLD.status = 'PENDING' AND NEW.status NOT IN ('VERIFIED', 'CANCELLED') THEN
        SIGNAL SQLSTATE '45000' 
        SET MESSAGE_TEXT = 'Invalid status transition from PENDING';
    ELSEIF OLD.status = 'VERIFIED' AND NEW.status NOT IN ('PACKED', 'CANCELLED') THEN
        SIGNAL SQLSTATE '45000'
        SET MESSAGE_TEXT = 'Invalid status transition from VERIFIED';
    ELSEIF OLD.status = 'PACKED' AND NEW.status NOT IN ('SHIPPED', 'CANCELLED') THEN
        SIGNAL SQLSTATE '45000'
        SET MESSAGE_TEXT = 'Invalid status transition from PACKED';
    ELSEIF OLD.status = 'SHIPPED' AND NEW.status NOT IN ('DELIVERED', 'CANCELLED') THEN
        SIGNAL SQLSTATE '45000'
        SET MESSAGE_TEXT = 'Invalid status transition from SHIPPED';
    ELSEIF OLD.status = 'DELIVERED' AND NEW.status != OLD.status THEN
        SIGNAL SQLSTATE '45000'
        SET MESSAGE_TEXT = 'Cannot change status of DELIVERED order';
    END IF;
    
    -- Clear tracking number if status becomes PENDING
    IF NEW.status = 'PENDING' THEN
        SET NEW.tracking_number = NULL;
    END IF;
END
$$
DELIMITER ;

DELIMITER $$
CREATE TRIGGER `auto_assign_label` AFTER INSERT ON `order_items` FOR EACH ROW BEGIN
    DECLARE product_category VARCHAR(50);
    DECLARE product_weight DECIMAL(10,2);
    DECLARE new_label VARCHAR(50);
    
    -- Get product information
    SELECT category, weight INTO product_category, product_weight
    FROM products
    WHERE product_id = NEW.product_id;
    
    -- Determine appropriate label
    IF product_category = 'Electronics' THEN
        SET new_label = 'Fragile Items';
    ELSEIF product_weight * NEW.quantity > 10 THEN
        SET new_label = 'Heavy Package';
    ELSEIF product_category = 'Components' THEN
        SET new_label = 'Temperature Sensitive';
    END IF;
    
    -- Update order label if not already set
    IF new_label IS NOT NULL THEN
        UPDATE orders
        SET label = COALESCE(label, new_label)
        WHERE order_id = NEW.order_id;
    END IF;
END
$$
DELIMITER ;
